In the MATTER OF the Appeal of the DENIAL OF Douglas F. CIOLEK'S APPLICATION FOR a FIREARMS PURCHASER. (Douglas F. Ciolek - Petitioner) C-832 September Term 2018
082561 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003510-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
